COPY public."ServiceOffer" (id, "categoryId", name, blurb, highlight, "order", visible, description, features, image, "priceNote") FROM stdin;
cmrnx5t2l000zt6iskcg2xt35	cmrnx5t2l000vt6is2sxcjdy3	Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)	Structured so ChatGPT and Perplexity cite you as the answer	t	3	t	Answer Engine Optimization structures your content so ChatGPT, Perplexity and Claude can cite your business when buyers ask for recommendations. We rewrite key pages answer-first, add FAQ and HowTo schema, build entity-consistent About and service pages, and track how often AI assistants mention you versus competitors. As more buying research moves into AI chat, AEO protects the demand your traditional SEO already earns — without waiting for a click that may never come.	{"Answer-first page restructuring","FAQ & HowTo schema markup","AI citation tracking & reports","Entity & brand consistency audit"}	\N	Bundled into SEO retainers from ₹15,000/mo — no separate fee
cmrnx5t2w0015t6is8yv7uu75	cmrnx5t2w0014t6isoiq1t6og	Google Ads	Search and Performance Max campaigns tuned for cost per lead	f	0	t	DigiSutra manages Google Ads campaigns end to end — Search, Performance Max and Shopping — built around cost per lead, not vanity clicks. As a Google Ads agency in Noida serving startups and SMBs in 12 countries, we handle keyword research, negative-keyword pruning, ad copy testing and bid strategy, with conversion tracking wired before a rupee is spent. Weekly optimization reports show exactly what your budget bought. Start with a free 15-page audit delivered in 48 hours.	{"Search + Performance Max campaign builds","Keyword and negative-keyword research","Ad copy and bid strategy testing","Weekly optimization + spend reports"}	\N	Management from ₹15,000/mo; campaigns live within 1–2 weeks
cmrnx5t2z001ct6is7jrnm5pw	cmrnx5t2z001bt6ish2oz6ygd	AI Chatbots	Website bots that answer, qualify and hand off to humans	t	0	t	AI chatbots for websites answer visitor questions instantly, qualify leads with smart follow-up questions, and hand hot prospects to your sales team — 24/7, without adding headcount. As an AI chatbot development company in Noida, DigiSutra builds bots trained on your actual pages, pricing and FAQs, powered by Claude or GPT, with clean human handoff and a lead log pushed to your CRM or WhatsApp. Start with our free 15-page audit, delivered in 48 hours.	{"Bot trained on your site content & FAQs","Lead capture pushed to CRM or WhatsApp","Human handoff rules for hot leads","Monthly transcript review & tuning"}	\N	Setup from ₹15,000; market ₹75k–₹4L for SMB bots. Live in 2–4 weeks
cmrnx5t2z001it6isio5aifi7	cmrnx5t2z001bt6ish2oz6ygd	AI Customer Support	Instant answers to most queries, humans for the rest	f	6	t	AI customer support resolves most routine queries — order status, pricing, returns, policies — instantly on your website and WhatsApp, freeing your team for the conversations that need a human. DigiSutra, an AI automation agency in Noida, trains the agent on your actual documents and past tickets, designs escalation rules so frustrated or high-value customers reach a person fast, and reviews transcripts monthly to close knowledge gaps. Hindi and English supported from day one.	{"Trained on your docs & past tickets","Website + WhatsApp, one knowledge base","Smart escalation to human agents","Hindi & English support built in"}	\N	Setup from ₹15,000; market ₹75k–₹4L for SMB support bots
cmrnx5t31001ot6isib0drkf3	cmrnx5t31001lt6isubjygk9w	Next.js/React Websites	Modern-stack sites that load fast and scale	t	2	t	Next.js and React websites built for speed: server-side rendering, static generation and image optimization engineered to keep Core Web Vitals in the green. DigiSutra develops modern-stack marketing and product sites with Tailwind CSS, clean component architecture and deployment on Vercel or your own infrastructure. The result is a site that feels instant on mobile data, handles traffic spikes without breaking, and gives search engines fast, crawlable pages. Get the free 15-page audit before you commit.	{"SSR/SSG with Next.js App Router","Core Web Vitals tuned before launch","Tailwind CSS component architecture","Vercel or self-hosted deployment"}	\N	Scoped per build from ₹35,000; typical delivery 4–6 weeks
cmrnx5t33001vt6iszenncjul	cmrnx5t33001ut6ismynhgqnp	CRM Setup	Zoho or HubSpot configured, migrated and adopted	f	0	t	CRM setup means your Zoho or HubSpot account configured, your leads migrated, and your team actually using it — typically live within 2–4 weeks. As a CRM implementation partner in Noida serving clients in 12 countries, DigiSutra handles custom fields, user roles, email and WhatsApp integration, and spreadsheet-to-CRM data migration, then trains your team so adoption sticks. You get a working system mapped to how you sell, not an empty license. Start with a free 15-page audit delivered in 48 hours.	{"Zoho or HubSpot fully configured","Data migration from spreadsheets","Email + WhatsApp integration","Team training and adoption support"}	\N	Implementations from ₹50,000 (market ₹75k–₹2.5L); 2–4 weeks
cmrnx5t350022t6isjxll6142	cmrnx5t350021t6iskirzssug	Logo Design	A custom mark with concepts, revisions and all formats	f	0	t	A professional logo design gives your business a custom mark that works everywhere — website, packaging, social media and print. DigiSutra's logo design process in Noida starts with a discovery brief, delivers three to four original concepts, refines your pick through structured revision rounds, and hands over every file format you will ever need: AI, EPS, SVG, PNG and favicon, plus basic usage guidelines. No templates, no stock marks — a logo built around your positioning, not this year's trend.	{"3–4 original logo concepts","Structured revision rounds","AI, EPS, SVG, PNG + favicon files","Basic usage guidelines included"}	\N	From ₹20,000 (agency market: ₹20k–₹75k); most logos in 2–3 weeks
cmrnx5t370029t6is8xjhn635	cmrnx5t370027t6isylctzfob	iOS Apps	Polished App Store builds that pass review first time	f	1	t	iOS app development that takes you from idea to App Store: native-quality builds on Flutter or React Native, designed to Apple's Human Interface Guidelines and submitted through App Store Connect for you. We handle provisioning, TestFlight beta distribution, in-app purchase and push notification setup, and the review checklist that trips up first-time founders. Startups in 12 countries ship their iPhone apps with us — one codebase, no separate native budget.	{"App Store Connect & TestFlight setup","HIG-compliant UI design","Push notifications & IAP wiring","Review-checklist submission support"}	\N	Included in cross-platform MVPs from ₹3,00,000; 8–12 weeks typical
cmrnx5t2l000wt6is3udgb8nb	cmrnx5t2l000vt6is2sxcjdy3	Technical SEO	Crawl, indexing and speed issues fixed so rankings can move	f	0	t	Technical SEO removes the crawl, indexing and speed issues that silently cap your rankings — fix the foundation and every other SEO effort works harder. We audit your site with Screaming Frog and Google Search Console, then repair broken redirects, duplicate content, thin pages, crawl budget waste and Core Web Vitals failures. You get a prioritized fix list, schema markup implementation and clean XML sitemaps, with every change documented so your developers can verify it.	{"Full crawl + indexation audit","Core Web Vitals & speed fixes","Schema markup implementation","Redirect & sitemap cleanup"}	\N	In SEO retainers from ₹15,000/mo; most fixes live in 2–4 weeks
cmrnx5t37002bt6is4pv9ctc1	cmrnx5t370027t6isylctzfob	React Native Apps	Share code with your React web app, ship faster	f	3	t	React Native app development that shares logic with your React website — if your web app is already React or Next.js, we reuse components, skills and even developers to ship your mobile app faster. We build with TypeScript and Expo where it fits, integrate REST or GraphQL APIs, and deliver Play Store and App Store builds from one codebase. A practical choice for SMBs across India that already run a React stack.	{"Code reuse from your React web app","TypeScript + Expo tooling","REST/GraphQL API integration","Both-store builds, one codebase"}	\N	Cross-platform MVPs from ₹3,00,000; typically 8–12 weeks
cmrpht3zm000gt6nkq25bnpts	cmrpht3zm000et6nk067ofh99	Security Monitoring	Threats caught before they become incidents	t	1	t	Round-the-clock website security monitoring catches malware injections, file changes, brute-force logins and blacklist flags before customers or Google see them. DigiSutra combines firewall rules (Cloudflare WAF), daily malware scans and file-integrity checks with human review from our Noida team, so alerts become fixes instead of noise. You get a monthly security report in plain language: what was blocked, what was patched, what needs a decision. It is the difference between finding a hack in hours and finding it in a search result.	{"24/7 malware & file-integrity scans","Cloudflare WAF & login hardening","Blacklist & SSL expiry watch","Monthly plain-English security report"}	\N	Part of care plans from ₹8,000/mo; market AMCs run ₹10k–₹25k/mo
cmrpht3zp000nt6nk7a5t6fau	cmrpht3zp000lt6nklw84lcmo	SEO Blog Writing	Answer-first articles Google and AI cite	t	1	t	SEO blog writing that leads with the answer — articles structured so Google, ChatGPT and AI Overviews can lift your paragraph as the response. Every post DigiSutra ships from its Noida studio is keyword-mapped, matched to search intent and built with clean H2/H3 structure, FAQ schema and internal links. You get research, briefs, human-edited drafts and on-page optimization in one workflow — no thin AI filler, and no ranking promises we can't stand behind.	{"Answer-first articles, 1,200–2,000 words","FAQ schema & internal links built in","Keyword & intent brief per post","Human-edited, plagiarism-checked drafts"}	\N	Core of retainers from ₹15,000/mo (market: ₹15k–₹40k/mo)
cmrpht3zs000ut6nkb8jgwpnv	cmrpht3zs000st6nkymmjn62k	SMS Campaigns	Time-sensitive offers straight to the pocket	f	1	t	Bulk SMS marketing that puts time-sensitive offers, reminders and alerts straight into your customers' pockets — messages most people read within minutes. DigiSutra manages the full stack for businesses across India: TRAI DLT registration, sender-ID and template approval, segmented sends via MSG91 or Twilio, and delivery reporting. Ideal for flash sales, appointment reminders and payment nudges where email is too slow. Get a free 15-page marketing audit in 48 hours to see where SMS fits your funnel.	{"TRAI DLT registration & compliance","Sender ID & template approvals","Segmented sends via MSG91/Twilio","Delivery & click reporting"}	\N	In programs from ₹10,000/mo; SMS platform & DLT fees billed at cost
cmrpht3zu0011t6nkuhsu18l5	cmrpht3zu000zt6nkoo4g2r9o	Campaign Strategy	Briefs, deliverables and timelines that stick	f	1	t	An influencer campaign strategy sets the goal, creator mix, content briefs, deliverables and posting timeline before anything goes live — so the campaign runs like a project, not a favour. We define target audience, platform split, hashtags, disclosure requirements and per-creator deliverables, then lock it in a written brief every creator signs off on. As an influencer marketing agency in Noida, we plan campaigns for startups and SMBs that need results they can report, not just likes.	{"Written campaign brief & goals","Creator mix & platform split","Deliverables and posting timeline","ASCI disclosure compliance built in"}	\N	Campaigns from ₹25,000; strategy locked in week one
cmrpht3zy0018t6nkhb00zt6b	cmrpht3zy0016t6nk0nnwrt5s	RAG Knowledge Assistants	AI that answers from your documents	t	1	t	RAG knowledge assistants let AI answer questions from your own documents — manuals, SOPs, product sheets, past tickets — instead of guessing from the open internet. We chunk and index your content in a vector database, wire retrieval into Claude or GPT, and add source citations so every answer is traceable. Ideal for support teams, HR policies and internal wikis. Hallucination testing and an update pipeline for new documents come with every build.	{"Vector database + document indexing","Source-cited, traceable answers","Works on PDFs, wikis and tickets","Update pipeline for new content"}	\N	From ₹75,000 depending on data volume; typical build 4–6 weeks
cmrpht402001ft6nke4fndsmk	cmrpht402001dt6nkus6ca6s3	Website + WhatsApp Coverage	One brain across both channels	f	1	t	One AI support agent covering both website chat and WhatsApp Business gives customers the same accurate answer on whichever channel they prefer. We deploy a single knowledge brain across both — WhatsApp Business API setup, approved message templates, and a matching web widget — so you maintain answers once, not twice. For Indian buyers who live on WhatsApp, this is usually the highest-traffic support channel from day one. Conversation logs from both channels feed one dashboard for review.	{"WhatsApp Business API setup + templates","Matching website chat widget","One knowledge base for both channels","Unified conversation logs"}	\N	Both channels covered in setups from ₹40,000; 2–4 weeks.
