cmrpht402001ht6nkmdl8nzbm	cmrpht402001dt6nkus6ca6s3	Knowledge Base Training	Answers from your docs, not the internet	f	3	t	Knowledge base training grounds your AI support agent in your own documents — help articles, policies, price lists, product specs — so it answers from facts you control instead of the open internet. We structure your content for retrieval (RAG), fill the gaps a bot exposes fast, and set the agent to say "I don't know" rather than invent. Updates are ongoing: change a policy, and the bot's answers change with it. Accuracy is reviewed against real transcripts each month.	{"Docs structured for RAG retrieval","Answers grounded in your content only","\\"Don't know\\" beats made-up replies","Monthly accuracy reviews"}	\N	Part of setups from ₹40,000; initial training in 1–2 weeks.
cmrpht402001it6nku95co890	cmrpht402001dt6nkus6ca6s3	Multilingual Replies	Hindi, English and more from one agent	f	4	t	Multilingual replies let one AI support agent handle Hindi, English, Hinglish and regional-language queries without separate bots or translated scripts. The agent detects the customer's language and answers in it, pulling from a single knowledge base — so serving customers across India doesn't multiply your maintenance work. We test tone and accuracy per language before launch, because a stiff machine-translated reply reads worse than no reply. Useful for D2C brands, clinics and service businesses with mixed-language audiences.	{"Auto language detection per chat","Hindi, English, Hinglish + more","One knowledge base, every language","Per-language tone and accuracy tests"}	\N	Included in setups from ₹40,000; extra languages add days, not lakhs.
cmrpht402001jt6nkpeg2xjtg	cmrpht402001dt6nkus6ca6s3	Support Analytics	What customers ask, what stumps the bot	f	5	t	Support analytics tell you what customers actually ask, what the AI resolves on its own, and which questions stump it — data most SMBs never had before a bot. You get a monthly report covering top query themes, resolution and handoff rates, and gaps to fix in your knowledge base; recurring complaints often point straight at product or pricing-page fixes. For DigiSutra clients in Noida and worldwide, this report doubles as free voice-of-customer research. It ships with every support-bot setup.	{"Monthly query-theme report","Resolution and handoff rates","Knowledge-gap flags to fix fast","Voice-of-customer insights included"}	\N	Bundled with every setup from ₹40,000; first report after month one.
\.
